<p>According to the mission of Montenegrin Journal of Sports Science and Medicine, there are contributions from all regions of the world that are published, thereby promoting international communication among scholars and professionals, and accordingly advertising in our journal (online or paper issues) will create, deepen and strengthen your relationship with your consumers - our readers.</p>

<p>Dedicated and enthusiastic professionals, buyers and decision-makers regarding your product or service will see your ads. </p>

<p><b>MJSSM online</b></p>

<p>MJSSM online offers the opportunity to target your products through banner and skyscraper advertising. There is a full range digital opportunities available:</p>

