<p><b>MJSSM print</b></p>

<p>MJSSM print offers the opportunity to present your product in journal decision makers within sports science and medicine. We guarantee your advertisement and message will stand out because of our high editorial to advertisement ratio. We can offer a range of loose or bound inserts, which can be targeted to the market you need to reach.</p>

